Name: handler

Synonyms: handler

Type: glossary

Description:
A group of <OpenXTalk> <statement|statements> that begin with an <on>,
<function>, <setProp>, or <getProp> <statement> and end with an <end>
<statement>. The basic unit of the <OpenXTalk|OpenXTalk> language.

References: on (control structure), setProp (control structure),
getProp (control structure), statement (glossary), OpenXTalk (glossary),
function (glossary), end (keyword)

